00:05:14.100 --> 00:05:18.820
data and say, we're just going to use all the new data coming in because we need that history.

00:05:18.820 --> 00:05:24.019
Because claims and accidents and life, depending on what area of insurance you're in,

00:05:24.660 --> 00:05:29.299
you really do need what we call a long tail or like a lot of historic data to predict what's

00:05:29.299 --> 00:05:34.179
