00:22:15.699 --> 00:22:23.859
tools? Yeah, I would say that the challenge, the resistance comes from a couple places, right? So

00:22:25.540 --> 00:22:31.300
Excel is what actuaries use. Actuaries love Excel. But they're also really smart,

00:22:31.300 --> 00:22:36.420
